{"tid":1452584,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"純討論 不是分化 有無人覺得唔好再dress code?","createTime":"2019-08-12T01:46:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T02:00:21.000Z","uid":25721,"like":4,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"09675317065c5110b1f27db8dbcb642ef92cd6ca","tid":1452584,"uid":25721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:46:17.000Z","msg":"我個人認為Dress Cide 真心無用， 係可以比人覺團結， 但！ 目標太大啦， 香港又細， 好易捉。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n預左比人屌<br />\n<br />\n但大家都係香港一份子<br />\n<br />\n我覺得要化整為零， 示威遊行勇武都可以出， 但試下唔好dress code?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d4bda91ed298d37072faa677f48a397f046449e","tid":1452584,"uid":28159,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:50:25.000Z","msg":"講咗好多次 black bloc係令前線難D俾人trace<br />\n唔洗你企上去, 但唔該唔好連著件衫都淆"},{"pid":"3922b9ec76728614364a61f2f75447873f45bb87","tid":1452584,"uid":25721,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"9d4bda91ed298d37072faa677f48a397f046449e","tid":1452584,"uid":28159,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:50:25.000Z","msg":"講咗好多次 black bloc係令前線難D俾人trace<br />\n唔洗你企上去, 但唔該唔好連著件衫都淆"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:54:31.000Z","msg":"真心咩？ 前線比人捉哂咁濟啦bor"},{"pid":"d75bdf2b154afa78bf9b78c4a1aad53cbd05fe3a","tid":1452584,"uid":201374,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"3922b9ec76728614364a61f2f75447873f45bb87","tid":1452584,"uid":25721,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"9d4bda91ed298d37072faa677f48a397f046449e","tid":1452584,"uid":28159,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:50:25.000Z","msg":"講咗好多次 black bloc係令前線難D俾人trace<br />\n唔洗你企上去, 但唔該唔好連著件衫都淆"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:54:31.000Z","msg":"真心咩？ 前線比人捉哂咁濟啦bor"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:56:15.000Z","msg":"黑衫唔係令到你喺現場難俾人捉<br />\n你令到你離開現場冇咁易俾人捉啊<br />\n勿忘新城市粉衫"},{"pid":"d72c08697b423c740b5dbf635523383533ecf802","tid":1452584,"uid":28159,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3922b9ec76728614364a61f2f75447873f45bb87","tid":1452584,"uid":25721,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"9d4bda91ed298d37072faa677f48a397f046449e","tid":1452584,"uid":28159,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:50:25.000Z","msg":"講咗好多次 black bloc係令前線難D俾人trace<br />\n唔洗你企上去, 但唔該唔好連著件衫都淆"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:54:31.000Z","msg":"真心咩？ 前線比人捉哂咁濟啦bor"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:58:42.000Z","msg":"捉哂唔代表trace到舉證<br />\n非法集結你著咩衫都走唔甩<br />\n但係襲擊同其他罪你真係要beyond a reasonable doubt證明到係嗰個人<br />\n總括而言你冇dress code唔見得俾有dress code有利<br />\n帶多件衫去同走換好過"},{"pid":"f50d4c493dec9fdcf4c1070531980829b8887ddd","tid":1452584,"uid":131836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:59:44.000Z","msg":"<strong>和理非新職系-影片認狗組</strong><br />\n<br />\n唔該大家有時間可以睇返之前d片<br />\n<br />\n將所有二五狗搵返出黎<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">清算警隊暴力 協助義士脫罪</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"54752c0fd2a4a78fb64f718cf58f5cdde5fab37c","tid":1452584,"uid":296350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:00:21.000Z","msg":"重新整理<br />\n記者可唔可以有共識！！<br />\n呢啲係我哋最關心嘅問題<br />\n<br />\n<strong>每日無論邊個問先，頭幾條都要係呢幾條！！<br />\n每一次問都數， 呢條問題係第幾次第幾日問，未有答案！ 幾時先會有答案？</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">請準備好每條問題嘅影片及圖片</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n1. 721點解唔執法？點解只告非法集會？點解全部未落charge？<br />\n播圖播片<br />\n指揮官喺村公所同白衣人對話，當時佢哋手持武器， 點解唔執法？<br />\n播片<br />\n<br />\n2 有證據顯示警方用過期Tear Gas?用咗幾多?點解用?<br />\n請準備圖及片<br />\nfollow up questions<br />\n過期催淚彈 成分變質變山埃， 警方會否道歉及賠償？<br />\n<br />\n3. 警察係咪扮示威者，然後執法？ 點解用咁嘅策略 ？點證明佢哋冇掉磚？冇煽動？冇放火？會否Charge佢哋參與暴動?<br />\n準備圖及片<br />\n<br />\n4. 點解會係地鐵站 內放催淚彈同胡椒彈？目的係驅趕定拘捕？<br />\n準備片<br />\nFollow up questions<br />\n如果係驅趕，佢哋已經喺地鐵站走緊！ 點解仲要放？ 如果係拘捕，你應該衝入去拉人而唔係放催淚彈胡椒彈！可唔可以解釋下<br />\n<strong>預設答案：</strong>情況混亂，個別事件<br />\nfollow up questions<br />\n警察冇專業訓練處理混亂情況？<br />\n個別例子係合理解釋？殺人放火強姦都係個別例子！ 示威者都係混亂情況下先做出唔尋常，唔理智行為，警方接唔接受呢個解釋唔落charge？<br />\n<br />\n5. 有片影到警察放武器入示威者背囊，點解？係唔係插贓嫁禍？<br />\n<strong>預設答案&nbsp;：</strong>&nbsp;冇資料<br />\n預備嗰條片， 講埋時間地點<br />\n叫佢解釋！<br />\n<br />\n6. 太古零距離開槍， 做法是否恰當？咩原因同情況下要咁做？<br />\n準備片<br />\n<br />\n7. 北角警察無視白衣人攻擊黑衣人及記者， 荃灣白衣人 一離場，場警察就進場，又係一個巧合？<br />\n準備片<br />\n<br />\n一齊畀意見！！<br />\n葵芳地鐵站內放催淚彈<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/chishing87/videos/10156292523426674/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fchishing87%2Fvideos%2F10156292523426674%2F&d=hP6DzN64O1sWLJLr9GARkSWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=80edeb56\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/chishing87/videos/10156292523426674/</a><br />\n<br />\n追打並推落扶手電梯<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkincident/permalink/2196364073824126\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2Fhkincident%2Fpermalink%2F2196364073824126&d=hP6DzN64O1sWLJLr9GARkSWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=bd44b4e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkincident/permalink/2196364073824126</a><br />\n<br />\n太古站開槍 1米內射示威者<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1178706375559427/posts/2424996360930416\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1178706375559427%2Fposts%2F2424996360930416&d=hP6DzN64O1sWLJLr9GARkSWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=208dddb2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1178706375559427/posts/2424996360930416</a><br />\n<br />\n竹支嫁禍<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1178706375559427/posts/2424974427599276\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1178706375559427%2F